name: geojson
raw_recipe:
package:
    name: geojson
    version: 1.3.2

source:
    fn: geojson-1.3.2.tar.gz
    url: https://pypi.python.org/packages/source/g/geojson/geojson-1.3.2.tar.gz
    md5: 27b75a4edbf9059e9aeb819eaad38593

build:
    number: 0
    preserve_egg_dir: True
    script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
    build:
        - python
        - setuptools
    run:
        - python

test:
    imports:
        - geojson

about:
    home: https://github.com/frewsxcv/python-geojson
    license: BSD License
    summary: Python bindings and utilities for GeoJSON

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - ocefpaf

about.summary: Python bindings and utilities for GeoJSON
